      <description>I would encourage NOT making a change to the inventory containers, as this would promote decentraliztion.&lt;br&gt;I would rather see players visit the tradeskill quarters of a zone (such as the bazaar special area), or visit the tradeskill quarters in the city zones.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Centralization allows people to interact with multiple tradeskillers.&lt;br&gt;Unlike the bazaar - tradeskillers have to be at their keyboard.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The create button needs to be locked out until both parties have agreed - preventing a tradeskiller from making a junk item whether intentional or accidental (agree / disagree toggles?).&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
